"title": "5333: healing",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5333",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The bringing about of a state of physical or spiritual health. Scripture recognises a close link between physical and spiritual health, with healing often being seen as an image of salvation in Christ.</p>\n<h2>God as the author of healing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:26\">EXO 15:26</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:2-Ps103:3\">PSA 103:2–103:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:15\">LUK 5:15</a></p>\n<h2>General aspects of healing</h2>\n<h3>Requests for healing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:1-2Kgs20:11\">2KI 20:1–20:11</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:24-2Chr32:26\">2CH 32:24–32:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:1-Isa38:8\">ISA 38:1–38:8</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:2\">2KI 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:14\">JAS 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Quarantine regulations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev12:1-Lev12:4\">LEV 12:1–12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:4\">LEV 13:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:26\">LEV 13:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:46\">LEV 13:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:8\">LEV 14:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:2\">NUM 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:19\">NUM 31:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs15:5\">2KI 15:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:12\">LUK 17:12</a></p>\n<h3>Healing results in discipleship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:52\">MRK 10:52</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:2\">JHN 6:2</a></p>\n<h3>Healing results in praise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:8-Acts3:9\">ACT 3:8–3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:12\">MRK 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:30-John9:33\">JHN 9:30–9:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:38\">JHN 9:38</a></p>\n<h2>Miraculous healing</h2>\n<h3>By Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:2-Matt8:3\">MAT 8:2–8:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">LUK 4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:27-Matt9:30\">MAT 9:27–9:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:34-Matt14:36\">MAT 14:34–14:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:53-Mark6:56\">MRK 6:53–6:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:21-Matt15:28\">MAT 15:21–15:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:24-Mark7:30\">MRK 7:24–7:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:32-Mark1:34\">MRK 1:32–1:34</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:40\">LUK 4:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:17-Luke6:19\">LUK 6:17–6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:48\">LUK 8:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:11\">LUK 9:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:19\">LUK 17:19</a></p>\n<h3>Through the prophets</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:17-1Kgs17:24\">1KI 17:17–17:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:29-2Kgs4:37\">2KI 4:29–4:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:10-2Kgs5:14\">2KI 5:10–5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Through the apostles</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:1\">MAT 10:1</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:1-Luke9:2\">LUK 9:1–9:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:6-Acts3:8\">ACT 3:6–3:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:15-Acts5:16\">ACT 5:15–5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:34\">ACT 9:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:8-Acts14:10\">ACT 14:8–14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:11-Acts19:12\">ACT 19:11–19:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:8-Acts28:9\">ACT 28:8–28:9</a></p>\n<h3>In the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:8-1Cor12:9\">1CO 12:8–12:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:17-Mark16:18\">MRK 16:17–16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:28\">1CO 12:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:30\">1CO 12:30</a></p>\n<h2>Healing of fever</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:15\">MAT 8:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:31\">MRK 1:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:39\">LUK 4:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:46-John4:54\">JHN 4:46–4:54</a></p>\n<h2>Healing of demon-possession</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:32-Matt9:33\">MAT 9:32–9:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:22\">MAT 12:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:1-Mark5:20\">MRK 5:1–5:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:17-Mark9:27\">MRK 9:17–9:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:38-Luke9:43\">LUK 9:38–9:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:16-Acts16:19\">ACT 16:16–16:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:11-Acts19:12\">ACT 19:11–19:12</a></p>\n<h2>Healing withheld</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:8-2Cor12:9\">2CO 12:8–12:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:20\">2TI 4:20</a></p>\n<h2>Medical treatments to bring healing</h2>\n<h3>Consulting doctors</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:12\">2CH 16:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:12\">MAT 9:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:22\">JER 8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:14\">COL 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>Taking medicine</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:23\">1TI 5:23</a></p>\n<h3>Disinfecting the house</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:41-Lev14:42\">LEV 14:41–14:42</a></p>\n<h3>Using splints</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek30:21\">EZK 30:21</a></p>\n<h3>Using bandages and oil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:6\">ISA 1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:34\">LUK 10:34</a></p>\n<h2>The spiritual significance of healing</h2>\n<h3>As an image of salvation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:4\">PSA 41:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:2-Ps103:5\">PSA 103:2–103:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:3\">PSA 147:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:22\">JER 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:19\">JER 14:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:14\">JER 17:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:12\">EZK 47:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:1\">HOS 6:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal4:2\">MAL 4:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:17\">MAT 8:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:4-Isa53:5\">ISA 53:4–53:5</a></p>\n<h3>Heaven is the place of ultimate healing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:4\">REV 21:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:18\">ROM 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:2\">REV 22:2</a></p>",
